{"tid":1310872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無安全，有人聽嘅嘅情緒支援熱線，我驚我會做傻事","createTime":"2019-07-13T01:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T08:05:51.000Z","uid":136686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e188da128602190611c39a9eed9c3c28521701b","tid":1310872,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係路過嘅畫家，放左工之後會出佔領區畫畫<br />\n<br />\n而家我嘅情緒好似一個鐘擺<br />\n有時想發癲，有時就拉住自己令自己唔好癲<br />\n<br />\n原本透過畫畫搵到一個平衡<br />\n最近返工比人調左去一個好多野做嘅位，要OT，上手仲留左一堆我搞唔掂嘅穌周屎<br />\n<br />\n放左工之後越來越攰，影響左畫畫嘅狀態<br />\n越畫越差<br />\n然後成個人好似骨牌咁冧左<br />\n<br />\n我想搵人傾計，我想跳樓！<br />\n我唔想返工！<br />\n<br />\n我驚打字太慢，我要比班同事聽到我想跳樓"},{"pid":"2fae20fc53cf61fb623723d20c6ea450b3a74a47","tid":1310872,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:47:55.000Z","msg":"畫自己個內心同啲負面野出黎，舒發一下情緒"},{"pid":"9abac09c17777ee58221da64dbdac23530c33eab","tid":1310872,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fae20fc53cf61fb623723d20c6ea450b3a74a47","tid":1310872,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:47:55.000Z","msg":"畫自己個內心同啲負面野出黎，舒發一下情緒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"有撚時間<br />\n我而家係公司<br />\n<br />\n有時間畫畫我不如畫靚女J下"},{"pid":"540541b446b0c08505806eacb5e1d879d4eaa4e5","tid":1310872,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:53:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個撒馬利亞根本係無人聽</span></span>"},{"pid":"e272e8513a36040ded51b2a809cf575fbcc14c54","tid":1310872,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"540541b446b0c08505806eacb5e1d879d4eaa4e5","tid":1310872,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:53:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個撒馬利亞根本係無人聽</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:55:03.000Z","msg":"連登大把兄弟會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/l